FBIS3-19472 "drweu052__a94018" FBIS-WEU-94-052-A Document Type:Daily Report 17 March 1993 ANNEX Germany No Bosnian Deportations Before 30 Sep AU1503182294 Hamburg DPA in German 1635 GMT 15 Mar 94--FOR OFFICIAL USE ONLY AU1503182294 Hamburg DPA Language: German Article Type:BFN [Text] Bonn -- The halt on the deportation of Bosnian refugees from Germany has been extended by six months to 30 September. A spokesman of the Interior Ministry confirmed in Bonn today that the interior ministers of the laender have agreed on this measure. Without this decision, the ban would have expired by the end of this month. The spokesman declined to comment on the number of refugees who are currently in Germany.
